{
  "page": "Leaf",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\">Leaf</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Leaf_by_Mattie_Victoria.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Leaf by Mattie Victoria.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/3f/Leaf_by_Mattie_Victoria.jpg/350px-Leaf_by_Mattie_Victoria.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"437\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/3f/Leaf_by_Mattie_Victoria.jpg/525px-Leaf_by_Mattie_Victoria.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/3f/Leaf_by_Mattie_Victoria.jpg/700px-Leaf_by_Mattie_Victoria.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Leaf, by Mattie Victoria ©</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Three-eyed_crow\" title=\"Three-eyed crow\">last greenseer</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Race</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Children_of_the_forest\" title=\"Children of the forest\">children of the forest</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/100_AC\" title=\"100 AC\">100&#160;AC</a> (roughly)<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (appears)</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">Played by</span></th><td>\nOctavia Alexandru (<a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones_-_Season_4\" title=\"Game of Thrones - Season 4\">Season 4</a>)<br />Kae Alexander (<a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones_-_Season_6\" title=\"Game of Thrones - Season 6\">Season 6</a>)</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">TV series</span></th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"Game of Thrones\">Game of Thrones</a></i>: <br /><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones_-_Season_4\" title=\"Game of Thrones - Season 4\">Season 4</a> | <a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones_-_Season_6\" title=\"Game of Thrones - Season 6\">6</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Leaf</b> is one of the <a href=\"/index.php/Children_of_the_forest\" title=\"Children of the forest\">children of the forest</a> in service to the <a href=\"/index.php/Three-eyed_crow\" title=\"Three-eyed crow\">last greenseer</a>. Her true name is too long for the human tongue.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>In the television adaptation <i><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"Game of Thrones\">Game of Thrones</a></i>, Leaf is portrayed by Octavia Alexandru in <a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones_-_Season_4\" title=\"Game of Thrones - Season 4\">Season 4</a> and Kae Alexander in <a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones_-_Season_6\" title=\"Game of Thrones - Season 6\">Season 6</a>. She was also portrayed by Doyin Ajiboye in the rejected pilot episode of <i><a href=\"/index.php/Bloodmoon\" title=\"Bloodmoon\">Bloodmoon</a></i>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance_and_Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance and Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Quotes_by_Leaf\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes by Leaf</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Quotes_about_Leaf\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes about Leaf</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Leaf&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">See also: <a href=\"/index.php/Category:Images_of_Leaf\" title=\"Category:Images of Leaf\">Images of Leaf</a></div>\n<p>Like the other children of the forest, Leaf is smaller than humans, but not childlike. She has nut-brown skin, dappled like a <a href=\"/index.php/Deer\" title=\"Deer\">deer</a>'s with paler spots. Her hands have only three fingers and a thumb, with sharp black claws instead of nails. She has large ears that can hear things that no man can hear.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> She has large gold and green eyes slitted like those of a <a href=\"/index.php/Cat\" title=\"Cat\">cat</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> allowing her to see in dark passages.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> Leaf's hair is a tangle of brown, red and gold, autumn colors, with vines and twigs and withered flowers woven through it. She wears a cloak of leaves.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php/Bran_Stark\" title=\"Bran Stark\">Bran Stark</a> thinks that from far away, Leaf looks no older than himself or his sisters, <a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa</a> or <a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya</a>, but close at hand, Leaf seems far older.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> Her voice is high and sweet, but also sad.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> She is the only one of the children in the <a href=\"/index.php/Cave_of_the_three-eyed_crow\" title=\"Cave of the three-eyed crow\">cave of the three-eyed crow</a> who speaks the <a href=\"/index.php/Common_Tongue\" title=\"Common Tongue\">Common Tongue</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Leaf&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Leaf_by_Kallielef.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/82/Leaf_by_Kallielef.jpg/350px-Leaf_by_Kallielef.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"442\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/82/Leaf_by_Kallielef.jpg/525px-Leaf_by_Kallielef.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/82/Leaf_by_Kallielef.jpg/700px-Leaf_by_Kallielef.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Leaf_by_Kallielef.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Leaf, by Kallielef ©</div></div></div>\n<p>Leaf was born in the time of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a>'s dynasty in the <a href=\"/index.php/Seven_Kingdoms\" title=\"Seven Kingdoms\">Seven Kingdoms</a>, and walked the world of men for two hundred years to watch, listen, and learn. She says she might be walking still, but her legs were sore and her heart was weary, so she turned her feet for home.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Leaf&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Leaf&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Outside the <a href=\"/index.php/Cave_of_the_three-eyed_crow\" title=\"Cave of the three-eyed crow\">cave of the three-eyed crow</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Beyond_the_Wall\" title=\"Beyond the Wall\">beyond the Wall</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Bran_Stark\" title=\"Bran Stark\">Bran Stark</a> and his companions — <a href=\"/index.php/Hodor\" title=\"Hodor\">Hodor</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Meera_Reed\" title=\"Meera Reed\">Meera</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Jojen_Reed\" title=\"Jojen Reed\">Jojen Reed</a> — are attacked by <a href=\"/index.php/Wight\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Wight\">wights</a>. A cloud of <a href=\"/index.php/Raven\" title=\"Raven\">ravens</a> pours from the cave, and Bran sees what appears to be a girl, almost like his sister <a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya</a>, chasing off the wights with the fire of a torch. Bran then realizes she is not a girl, but a child of the forest, who leads them into the cave of the <a href=\"/index.php/Last_greenseer\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Last greenseer\">last greenseer</a>, Lord Brynden.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The little woman explains about the children of the forest to Bran and his companions, calling them \"those who sing the song of earth\". She explains that the children in the cave have names too long for the human tongue, so Bran and Meera give them names. Meera calls the little woman Leaf. Leaf warns the company not to wander too far in the cave because of its dangers, saying that not even her people have explored all its passages despite living there for a thousand thousand years.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Leaf helps Lord Brynden train Bran as a <a href=\"/index.php/Greenseer\" title=\"Greenseer\">greenseer</a>, giving him <a href=\"/index.php/Weirwood_paste\" title=\"Weirwood paste\">weirwood paste</a>. When Bran sees a <a href=\"/index.php/Vision\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Vision\">vision</a> of his late father, <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a>, Leaf warns Bran not to try to call him back from death.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_by_Leaf\">Quotes by Leaf</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Leaf&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes by Leaf\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Men, they are the children.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Leaf, to <a href=\"/index.php/Bran_Stark\" title=\"Bran Stark\">Bran Stark</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Bran:</b> Where are the rest of <a href=\"/index.php/Children_of_the_forest\" title=\"Children of the forest\">you</a>?<br />\n<b>Leaf:</b> Gone down into the earth. Into the stones, into the trees. Before the <a href=\"/index.php/First_Men\" title=\"First Men\">First Men</a> came all this land that you call <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a> was home to us, yet even in those days we were few. The <a href=\"/index.php/Old_gods\" title=\"Old gods\">gods</a> gave us long lives but not great numbers, lest we overrun the world as <a href=\"/index.php/Deer\" title=\"Deer\">deer</a> will overrun a wood where there are no <a href=\"/index.php/Wolves\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Wolves\">wolves</a> to hunt them. That was in the dawn of days, when our sun was rising. Now it sinks, and this is our long dwindling. The <a href=\"/index.php/Giant\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Giant\">giants</a> are almost gone as well, they who were our bane and our brothers. The great <a href=\"/index.php/Lion\" title=\"Lion\">lions</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">western hills</a> have been slain, the <a href=\"/index.php/Unicorn\" title=\"Unicorn\">unicorns</a> are all but gone, the <a href=\"/index.php/Mammoth\" title=\"Mammoth\">mammoths</a> down to a few hundred. The <a href=\"/index.php/Direwolves\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Direwolves\">direwolves</a> will outlast us all, but their time will come as well. In the world that men have made, there is no room for them, or us.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Bran_Stark\" title=\"Bran Stark\">Bran Stark</a> and Leaf</cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_about_Leaf\">Quotes about Leaf</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Leaf&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes about Leaf\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>That was not <a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya's</a> voice, nor any child's. It was a woman's voice, high and sweet, with a strange music in it like none that he had ever heard and a sadness that he thought might break his heart.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Bran_Stark\" title=\"Bran Stark\">Bran Stark</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Leaf&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i>See the <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest/Calculations_Ages_(Continued2)#Leaf\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest/Calculations Ages (Continued2)\">Leaf</a> calculation.</i></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\">2.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\">2.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-4\">2.4</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-5\">2.5</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-6\">2.6</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-7\">2.7</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_34\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 34\">Chapter 34</a>, Bran III.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">3.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\">3.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\">3.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-3\">3.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-4\">3.4</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-5\">3.5</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-6\">3.6</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dra